{"tid":2040831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"逾30休班懲教員飯聚賀升職　涉違限聚令　懲署：轉介調查","createTime":"2020-05-29T00:07:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T10:31:43.000Z","uid":175194,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ff08fcbf32e985822a78deb24bffb0a5efde2818","tid":2040831,"uid":175194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:07:06.000Z","msg":"疫情稍為緩和，政府未敢鬆懈。懲教署署長胡英明上周向傳媒表示，「最核心工作就是防疫」，話音未落，就有懲教人員涉嫌違反限聚令。<br />\n<br />\n《香港01》直撃逾30名休班懲教人員，上周四（21日）晚在長沙灣富臨漁港酒家貴賓房飯聚，飯局未開始眾人已除低口罩，聚集聊天及打麻雀，期間更有人吸食雪茄和香煙。當晚數名軍裝警員兩度到場調查，不過逗留數分鐘後離開，無作檢控。<br />\n<br />\n懲教署承認，聚會屬於小欖院所休班人員的私人飯局，已將事件轉介執法機構調查，惟未交代涉事人數及職級。警方則稱，到場時發現餐桌分隔距離符合要求，無超過八名顧客用餐，事件中無人被票控。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc3f83f41b7f84a6a169db9531ce17acdeee6a43","tid":2040831,"uid":175194,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:12:00.000Z","msg":"犯法就係犯法"},{"pid":"73521fa07027ca78af783bfeee2fab334e1eee64","tid":2040831,"uid":108305,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:12:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1075d5fa1b9baffec5e9f0d4752f6ddc7e9c8c26","tid":2040831,"uid":175194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73521fa07027ca78af783bfeee2fab334e1eee64","tid":2040831,"uid":108305,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:12:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:13:39.000Z","msg":"即管睇下結果點"},{"pid":"046433bc47cd04224c1b14c64bdf36d675d49fc8","tid":2040831,"uid":21028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T00:14:26.000Z","msg":"因為你哋唔係狗隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53034ac582b6fd8939eab89909bb1c009974f390","tid"